column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Hilmar is offering good coin for a seemingly simple task.
Fill the mining lamps with pungent lamp oil.
Are you busy? Didn't think so.
I'm offering coin to anyone willing to fill up the lamps. Interested?
There are four of them. Here's the oil. Come and see me when you're done.
I'd like it done now, if you don't mind.
Finally finished, then. Gnomes didn't get in your way, did they?
There seem to be more and more of them these days. Makes even filling the lamps a pain in the arse.
Still, can't let them stop us from doing our jobs. Just another occupational hazard.
Anyway, here's your pay. Good work, sinner.
